events.title: Scholarly Resources for Teaching event 001
events.description:
UNSW Library is hosting an online Scholarly Resources for Teaching Week with events from X to Y, 2021.

Targeted subject area online sessions will be presented by experts from the publishers themselves, with a focus on use of the product resources in teaching and learning at UNSW.

Library staff will also be there to answer your questions about linking the resources in Leganto. Sessions will be recorded and the link sent to staff who have registered for a session.
